r loved ones completely safe when using your garage door.";i:53;s:127:"Garage door roller keeps coming off track For more information visit our website For 24 hr emergency repairs Call 281 501-6497.";i:54;s:36:"Services Garage Door Repair Service.";i:55;s:87:"Op very likely your tracks are crooked as hell or one of your cables came off its path.";i:56;s:182:"The door is basically trying to ride into a corner of the path and the lateral force of that from last last couple feet causes the roller to pop out as it travels through the radius.";i:57;s:236:"The main reason to cause the door to go off-track from one bad roller or several bad rollers is the fact that if the door does not roll up and down properly in the opener is going to have a hard time opening and closing the garage door.";i:58;s:107:"In other words if the garage opener cannot open the door Then it can make the cables jump off of the cable.";}}